				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">God no.  The earth pet is our greatest utility pet, it is the only method we have of playing CC, saving wiping raids, save dumb chanters.  
<br />

<br />
Remember, our earth pet can root EVERYTHING that the root doesn't get resisted on.  If a mob has too high of MR or it is too high of level it will not root it, but everything else it does.  
<br />

<br />
In responce to Kirium's post, the earth pet is able to root everything in fire, vexd and tipt.  Just debuff it first, sure the root gets resisted occasionally by the high MR mobs, but when it lands it will root.
<br />

<br />
I have used the earth pet in uncountable groups to save from a wipe.  I have used an earth pet to save several raids from wiping.  He was incredibly useful in Time P1 when tanks got bugged and couldn't zone in, he was a lifesaver in Ikkinz trial 3 on the splitters.  He is the only way besides DPS we can contribute to the make or break of a raid.
<br />

<br />
Kopla
<br />
MM Server</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
