<br />
This would be nice, but will never happen.  It would be the ultimate form of agro kiting.
<br />

<br />
Snare isn't broken by nuking, so basically you hve the earth pet 100% snare it, and start nuking as hard as possible.  The mob will TRY and go for you, and will completely ignore the pet.  And the pet massacres it.  Just nuke enough to keep it's attention focused on you and the pet never gets hit.  And you don't need to run around either.  Just sit on the ground and med up, and throw the occasional nuke.
<br />

<br />
So it will never happen.  Sure the agro-kiters do it, but they at least have to have enough room to move around.  With this, mages could agro-kite anywhere because of 100% snare.  It wouldn't be kiting, but the mob would never hit anything.
<br />

<br />
Extend this to groups.  No melees, only ranged.  Have the earth pet go in, and then make sure that it never gets agro.  Kill ANYTHING that can't one-round the pet easily.
<br />

